* Add DEseq DGE analysis
* Add dynamic mechanism to extend ROGEr by other modules:
  roger add-dge-method-ma betterLimma /path/to/betterLimma.R # will execute betterLimma.R with all required data exported to a temp file
  roger add-ges-method hdCAMERA /path/to/hdCAMERA.R
